{"tid":535091,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我放棄咗","createTime":"2018-01-20T13:18:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-13T03:43:41.000Z","uid":106944,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"4692e8f1175192f40950cecb27575fad8d7fff3a","tid":535091,"uid":106944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:18:19.000Z","msg":"我好很羨慕啲人唔洗經歷過啲咩就可以擁有一段好好嘅感情<br />\n<br />\n啲人成日會話咩識咗而家個男/女朋友之後覺得以前經歷過嘅所有野都抵曬<br />\n<br />\n屌你啦<br />\n我以前都信過 我而家已經唔鳩信<br />\n<br />\n反正大家都係各取所需 不過其中一方擺咗真心落去咋嘛 <br />\n<br />\n咁咪蝕底囉 受傷個個係你咋嘛<br />\n<br />\n我都係女仔 我都曾經幻想過會有人好好咁對你 曾經鄙視個啲玩玩下拍散拖嘅人<br />\n<br />\n我諗呢個世界真係有啲人好似我咁 身上有啲令人好快厭嘅特質 <br />\n<br />\n呢種特質其實連我自己都發覺 如果我係男仔 同我一齊一定好快厭<br />\n<br />\n於是我慢慢都麻木咗 其實拍散拖都無乜所謂 <br />\n<br />\n我地唔洗放真感情 咁咪唔會受傷 係咪？<br />\n<br />\n唔再在乎 我覺得我嘅人生好過咗好多"},{"pid":"91d31e3cd13016fa85c5bb6c26d8c496fa7500bc","tid":535091,"uid":85418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:20:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb33fc40a4d0586760156992784adf7d54444a9","tid":535091,"uid":57835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-20T13:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae7fb5b1bb28efe3f543efc95a193e73f4dbcd24","tid":535091,"uid":27632,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T07:59:28.000Z","msg":"Ching，加油"},{"pid":"d0b85c4fb4662250b61175cdf318912d837299f0","tid":535091,"uid":144063,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T08:10:27.000Z","msg":"有冇放棄埋右?"},{"pid":"11c6de66e1a2115744a013674e6992078c3b0d4a","tid":535091,"uid":106944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0b85c4fb4662250b6